00:00:19,208 --> 00:00:24,583
Inori's Void. Once he does, we
seize that second truck ASAP.

3
00:00:24,666 --> 00:00:26,875
The target will reach
the attack point in

4
00:00:26,958 --> 00:00:33,708
six, five, four,
three, two, one!

5
00:00:33,791 --> 00:00:34,916
Go!

6
00:00:41,375 --> 00:00:42,833
Shu, engage them!

7
00:00:42,916 --> 00:00:46,375
Get your ass in gear already!
They're going to see us!

8
00:00:46,458 --> 00:00:48,791
Just pull the Void!

9
00:00:48,875 --> 00:00:49,791
I can't!

10
00:00:49,875 --> 00:00:51,333
Dammit! They're onto us!

11
00:00:54,291 --> 00:00:57,166
Shu! What's wrong? Talk to me!

12
00:00:59,375 --> 00:01:01,166
If you don't move, they're dead!

13
00:01:01,250 --> 00:01:02,750
We need you right now!

14
00:01:02,833 --> 00:01:04,083
Please, Shu.

15
00:01:08,708 --> 00:01:10,083
No, come back!

16
00:01:11,958 --> 00:01:15,125
All units, this is Gai!
Abort the mission! Repeat!

17
00:01:15,208 --> 00:01:16,791
Abort the mission!

18
00:02:49,666 --> 00:02:55,333
Blooming wildflower--

19
00:02:55,416 --> 00:02:57,833
Tell me, Shu, do you love me?

20
00:02:57,916 --> 00:02:59,708
Course I do!

21
00:02:59,791 --> 00:03:03,333
Then promise me, that you'll
make your big sister happy.

22
00:03:06,333 --> 00:03:14,833
