The two overlapped.

24
00:03:40,791 --> 00:03:44,250
Hey! Are you awake?
I'm coming up!

25
00:03:44,333 --> 00:03:47,750
Rise and shine, Shu!
Did you sleep okay?

26
00:03:47,833 --> 00:03:49,416
Yeah.

27
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:51,125
Here!

28
00:03:51,208 --> 00:03:53,250
I grabbed you a breakfast
sandwich on the way,

29
00:03:53,333 --> 00:03:54,958
does that sound all right?

30
