64
00:06:09,375 --> 00:06:13,958
Still, I wonder what Keido's
playing at. He steals this,

65
00:06:14,041 --> 00:06:15,458
and then instead
of running for it,

66
00:06:15,541 --> 00:06:17,791
he waltzes straight
into custody?

67
